snippet.title: Weird Dice
snippet.description:
We're all used to rolling a pair of dice and getting anything from snake-eyes (2) to boxcars(12). Want to see a pair of weird dice that produce the same distribution as regular dice? Watch this video to discover the Sicherman Dice.


Twitter: @TPointMath


Music:

"Casa Bossa Nova" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
